dyform.formProp.relation.helpMsg.zh:
映射关系表示当前表与所选择的表之间的关系:
 一对一: 表示当前表和被选择表数据是一一对应关系;
 一对多: 表示当前表一条数据对应被选择表多条数据;
 多对一: 表示当前表多条数据对应被选择表1条数据;
 多对多: 表示当前表1条数据对应被选择表多条,
        反之被选择表的一条数据也对于当前表的多条数据。

dyform.formProp.relation.helpMsg.en:
Mapping relationship represents the relationship between the current table and the selected table:
 One-to-One: One-to-one correspondence between current table and selected table data;
 One-to-Many: One record in current table corresponds to multiple records in selected table;
 Many-to-One: Multiple records in current table correspond to one record in selected table;
 Many-to-Many: One record in current table corresponds to multiple records in selected table,
        and vice versa.

dyform.utils.dbList.fieldCompTypesMsg.en:
Type operation tips:
1. By default, numeric fields are mapped to number input components;
   String fields are mapped to single-line input components;
   Date fields are mapped to date picker components;
2. If fields have special business needs, they can be configured to corresponding component types

dyform.utils.dbList.configMsg.en:
Operation guide:
1. This configuration is mainly for field display, excluded fields and component types;
2. Table fields need to be configured before being added to the stage,
   otherwise the configuration will not take effect;
3. Other detailed configurations need to be handled on the stage
